    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411010/extras/b23002f0fde0fb2a18c1ab529981a74c.avif?t=1772170677\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蒸汽文明被巨大的灾难毁灭，幸存的人类带着残破的机器进入了曾经的禁地。操控巨大的蒸汽陆行方舟，建造移动的城市，探索这个神秘危险的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >方舟军团是一款结合了策略RTS和生存建造玩法的游戏。如果有任何问题可以加入QQ群261293882,我们会尽力为您解答问题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造巨大的方舟</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >方舟内部可以自由改造舱室功能。同一个舱室内可以摆放不同的设备。建立一条高效的生产线，或是打造一个舒适的生活舱，一切都看你的规划。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411010/extras/1a4b6580283b6fc3912c5c86b4b94eff.poster.avif?t=1772170677\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411010/extras/1a4b6580283b6fc3912c5c86b4b94eff.webm?t=1772170677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411010/extras/1a4b6580283b6fc3912c5c86b4b94eff.mp4?t=1772170677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索广袤的世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界地图由超过三万个六角格地块组成。地块中不同的地形、生物、资源、物品、遗迹等内容构成了这个丰富多彩的世界。狩猎生物、采集资源、探索遗迹、捡拾物品都可以让你的方舟越来越强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411010/extras/c49882a4d2749d2998d1e8bfd65df0c6.poster.avif?t=1772170677\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411010/extras/c49882a4d2749d2998d1e8bfd65df0c6.webm?t=1772170677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411010/extras/c49882a4d2749d2998d1e8bfd65df0c6.mp4?t=1772170677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在城市之间贸易</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不同派系建立的城市间穿梭，充满危险的贸易路线会带来丰厚的回报。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411010/extras/c70f743b0a0012f4f2563bc53daf805d.poster.avif?t=1772170677\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411010/extras/c70f743b0a0012f4f2563bc53daf805d.webm?t=1772170677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411010/extras/c70f743b0a0012f4f2563bc53daf805d.mp4?t=1772170677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >铁与火的战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >盗贼的劫掠、贸易联盟的反击都会引发战斗。既有方舟之间的火炮对射，也有舱室内激烈的白刃战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411010/extras/593a5d873e34b7b9b6838275178b57fd.poster.avif?t=1772170677\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411010/extras/593a5d873e34b7b9b6838275178b57fd.webm?t=1772170677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411010/extras/593a5d873e34b7b9b6838275178b57fd.mp4?t=1772170677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_parag